/>\n（但我覺得其實kid lulu 陳漢典主持都好麻麻）<br />\n<br />\nBTW 唔知點解就算係同一個主持<br />\neg 陶晶瑩佢係台灣同大陸都有大學生了沒<br />\n但我總係覺得大陸嘅綜藝冇咁好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都唔會點睇</blockquote><br />\n音樂似06 07果時嘅香港，人仲有，甚至有新星出，但你話突出真係冇邊幾個<br />\n電影其實已經開始落，hardcore果d冇人睇，那些年果種超級商業片又冇人頂到/或者搵到件新偶像"},{"pid":"750276307c36b9f3ff414eeaae254e698a8ee6a9","tid":143133,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"10年前左右好正&hellip;&hellip;劇唔洗講，有個遊戲節目叫嚦咕嚦咕樂翻天，睇得好撚過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68a7e55a4533b0dfc7911546fcbf313b3573cdb","tid":143133,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"見到台灣娛樂圈好似十年前香港咁真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1647eb5f4d5936e496effbe866a3dcfc9d84b7","tid":143133,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"香港仲有廣東話市場<br />\n但國語市場比大陸食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1891cc08ae3beff8b88cb6ed276462272e72459a","tid":143133,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"支那用錢摧毁緊港臺文化,"},{"pid":"cef1338b3b19a46278bb5b3771fa93d4fa6f580f","tid":143133,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港仲有廣東話市場<br />\n但國語市場比大陸食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得相反，香港人自己本身已經好多唔聽廣東歌，而就算少左台灣人聽國語歌，大陸狗都會聽"},{"pid":"7809c31816901d69782b2dc97898f9450ef6aaca","tid":143133,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那用錢摧毁緊港臺文化,</blockquote><br />\n自己積弱先係問題，人地掟錢都係買top，如果人地買哂d top，你冇人接到，本身自己都有問題"},{"pid":"60101a1e30d14dae3e0a247e438108712d5481d4","tid":143133,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03